casebody.data:
No. 73,

Orig.

California v. Nevada.

Preliminary Report of Special Master received, ordered filed, and adopted by the Court. Accordingly, motion of California State Assemblyman Mike Cullen for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae, motion of the State of Nevada for leave to file an amended answer setting forth a counterclaim, and motion of the State of California for leave to file an amended complaint granted. [For earlier order herein, see 433 U. S. 918.]
